{
  "stem": "22803.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one of the other things that they did in the school was that for six weeks, I were sent to learn nursing-- not nursing care-- like a children's nursery, you know, child care and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when the other non-Jewish children went to, to a hospital where they learned about taking care of babies, I was sent to a Jewish home which was orphanage.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was partly for an orphanage, or also a home for maybe working mothers, you know, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was sent there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And while I was there was when Kristallnacht occurred.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the night-- that's why I mentioned before about living across from Hitler-- possibly because of living there, nothing occurred in our neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the synagogue-- I should still say, the synagogue in Munich was torn down some years earlier because they decided they going need a garage, a parking-- what do you-- not a parking garage, but the parking lot for the German-- the House of German Kunst, you know, art exhibit or whatever.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tore down the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in my neighborhood, which was residential, nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the next morning, I went to school to that orphanage where I was supposed to take care of babies and children.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometime in the morning, this lady, who I said had at one time lived with my parents, this Chinese-- the wife of this Chinese doctor, came to pick me up from school.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because this was the morning after Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I guess when it became-- oh, we had no radio in those days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So by-- by-- I guess by the time they found out something was going on, they had to bring me home from school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was fetched to come home from school.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
